"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-olympic-table-tennis-rules-paris-2024\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The summer Olympics have arrived, and you know what that means\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094table tennis at the absolute highest level!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The summer Olympics\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 19}, {\"ngram\": \"the absolute highest level\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether you are an enjoyer ofForrest Gump,Balls of Fury, or merely grew up with an easily accessible ping-pong table there are myriad reasons to get excited to watch table tennis at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 307, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an enjoyer\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 135}, {\"ngram\": \"Gump\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 150}, {\"ngram\": \"Balls\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 156}, {\"ngram\": \"Fury\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 164}, {\"ngram\": \"an easily accessible ping-pong table\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 225}, {\"ngram\": \"myriad reasons\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"table tennis\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 287}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, the rules are a little different for the Olympics than in Grandpa's garage playing a family tournament at Thanksgiving.\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 378, \"end\": 385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grampa_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9974440379446439, \"rank\": 0.002562511738313475, \"text\": \"Grandpa\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grampa_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grampa_Simpson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"a family tournament\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"Thanksgiving\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The basics are familiar, insofar as the objective of the game is to defeat the opponent by earning points in a manner quite like tennis.\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The basics\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"the objective\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 489}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"the opponent\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"points\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"a manner\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the particulars are where Olympic table tennis diverges from the games that take place in Bryant Park.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the particulars\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic table tennis\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 627}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"Bryant Park\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here we endeavor to inform you of those differences and paint a full picture of what table tennis will look like at the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those differences\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"a full picture\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"what table tennis\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Visually, Olympic table tennis is not all that dissimilar from standard ping-pong.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic table tennis\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"standard ping-pong\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Games are played on a rectangular table, split into two halves by a short net that checks in at 15.25 centimeters, per Olympic regulations.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Games\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"a rectangular table\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"two halves\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"a short net\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"15.25 centimeters\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic regulations\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The paddle is more commonly referred to as a \\\"racquet\\\" in international play and boasts two rubber sides\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 one black and one red.\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The paddle\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"racquet\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"international play\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"two rubber sides\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ball itself will either be orange or white with a weight of 2.7 grams and a diameter of 40 millimeters.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ball\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"a weight\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"2.7 grams\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"a diameter\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"40 millimeters\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To determine who goes first, table tennis turns to a classic\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094an old-fashioned toin coss.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"table tennis\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"a classic\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094an old-fashioned toin coss\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The umpire will flip a coin and the winner will get to choose whether they'd like to serve first, receive first, or choose a side of the table, at which point the decision to serve or receive will fall on the loser of the coin toss.\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The umpire\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"a coin\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"the winner\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"a side\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"which point\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"the loser\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the coin toss\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once the order of operations is determined by the coin toss, the game will get underway by one player serving to the other.\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the order\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"operations\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"the coin toss\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"one player\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there are rules in place to prevent any sort of trickery from occurring on the serve.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rules\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"any sort\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"trickery\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"the serve\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to theOlympics website, \\\"The server has to hold the ball with an open palm, toss it up and strike it in a manner that the ball bounces first on the server\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s side of the table before bouncing over the net to the other side.\\\"\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOlympics website\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"The server\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"an open palm\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"a manner\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"the server\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s side\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"the net\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"the other side\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In singles, the server is permitted to hit the ball to any part of the table.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"the server\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"any part\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In doubles, though, all serves must go diagonally across the table.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"doubles\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"all serves\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2176}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, on returns, a player must wait until the ball is bounced to hit it with a paddle.\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"returns\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"a player\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"a paddle\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If they hit it while still in the air, a foul is called.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"a foul\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ultimate objective is for one player to reach the target score quicker than the other.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ultimate objective\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"one player\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"the target score\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In order to do that, points must be scored.\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"points\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A point is scored in two different ways.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2537, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A point\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"two different ways\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first way for a player to score a point is to hit the ball to an area where the opponent cannot return it.\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first way\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"a player\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"an area\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"the opponent\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doing so will earn the hitting player a point, so long as the ball legally bounces off the table on the side of the opponent first.\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hitting player\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2686}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"the side\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"the opponent\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A point is also scored if an opponent hits the ball into the net or misses the table entirely.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A point\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"an opponent\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2819}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"the net\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In that scenario the receiving player, not the hitting player, gets a point for their opponent's miscue.\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that scenario\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"the receiving player\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"not the hitting player\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2938}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram\": \"their opponent's miscue\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 2980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In order to win a match of Olympic table tennis, one player must reach 11 points before the other.\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"a match\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic table tennis\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3030}, {\"ngram\": \"one player\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"11 points\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an instance where the score is tied, 10-10, the first player to reach 11 willnotwin.\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an instance\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3096}, {\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"the first player\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3145}, {\"ngram\": \"11 willnotwin\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, the winner will be the first player to go up bytwopoints.\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the winner\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3189}, {\"ngram\": \"the first player\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But one win does not secure a full Olympic victory.\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one win\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3249}, {\"ngram\": \"a full Olympic victory\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In singles, table tennis games are usually best-of-seven matches.\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"table tennis games\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3320}, {\"ngram\": \"best-of-seven matches\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So the first player to get to 11 points (or win by two) four times will be declared winner of the game.\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first player\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3375}, {\"ngram\": \"11 points\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"four times\", \"from\": 3412, \"to\": 3422}, {\"ngram\": \"winner\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3446}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The best way to fully understand the concepts above is to see them in action.\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The best way\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3473}, {\"ngram\": \"the concepts\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thus, we present a 10-minute highlight compilation of Olympic table tennis.\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 10-minute highlight compilation\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3589}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic table tennis\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are now fully prepared to enjoy Olympic table tennis.\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic table tennis\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Loading recommendations\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations Liam McKeone is a senior writer for the Breaking and Trending News team at Sports Illustrated.\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3766, \"end\": 3770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Gallagher\", \"score\": 0.9999999953024599, \"rank\": 4.6723667791864e-09, \"text\": \"Liam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Gallagher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Gallagher\"}, {\"begin\": 3841, \"end\": 3859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2031694443439676e-18, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"personalized content recommendations\", \"from\": 3728, \"to\": 3764}, {\"ngram\": \"a senior writer\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3796}, {\"ngram\": \"the Breaking and Trending News team\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been in the industry as a content creator since 2017, and prior to joining SI in May 2024, McKeone worked for NBC Sports Boston and The Big Lead.\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 4013, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3978, \"end\": 3995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports_Boston\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Sports Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265